export const Night = (props: React.SVGProps<SVGSVGElement>) => (
  <svg
    fill='#00FFFF'
    width='14px'
    height='14px'
    viewBox='0 0 36 36'
    version='1.1'
    preserveAspectRatio='xMidYMid meet'
    xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'
    {...props}
  >
    <g id='SVGRepo_bgCarrier' strokeWidth='0' />
    <g
      id='SVGRepo_tracerCarrier'
      strokeLinecap='round'
      strokeLinejoin='round'
    />
    <g id='SVGRepo_iconCarrier'>
      <title>moon-solid</title>
      <path d='M29.2,26.72A12.07,12.07,0,0,1,22.9,4.44,13.68,13.68,0,0,0,19.49,4a14,14,0,0,0,0,28,13.82,13.82,0,0,0,10.9-5.34A11.71,11.71,0,0,1,29.2,26.72Z' />
      <rect x='0' y='0' width='36' height='36' fillOpacity='0' />
    </g>
  </svg>
)
